  <main class="policy-content">

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>Return Policy</h2>
      
      <div class="alert alert-success">
        <strong>Returns Accepted:</strong> We accept returns on eligible LUNVYR lighting fixtures within 30 days of delivery, provided you notify us within 48 hours of receiving your order.
      </div>

      <h3>Return Eligibility</h3>
      <p>To be eligible for return, items must meet the following criteria:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>48-Hour Notification:</strong> You must contact us within 48 hours of delivery to initiate the return process</li>
        <li><strong>30-Day Window:</strong> Physical return must be completed within 30 days of delivery</li>
        <li><strong>Original Condition:</strong> Item must be unused, undamaged, and in original packaging</li>
        <li><strong>Standard Products:</strong> Only applies to our standard collection pieces (custom orders excluded)</li>
        <li><strong>All Components:</strong> Must include all original hardware, instructions, and accessories</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Non-Returnable Items</h3>
      <p>The following items cannot be returned:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Custom or made-to-order pieces with specific modifications</li>
        <li>Items damaged by customer installation or use</li>
        <li>Products returned after the 30-day window</li>
        <li>Items missing original packaging or components</li>
        <li>Special finishes or custom color requests</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Why the 48-Hour Notification?</h3>
      <p>The 48-hour notification requirement allows us to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Quickly address any immediate concerns or issues</li>
        <li>Provide installation support that might resolve concerns</li>
        <li>Ensure proper documentation for return processing</li>
        <li>Maintain quality control and customer satisfaction records</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>How to Return</h2>
      
      <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <strong>Important:</strong> You must notify us within 48 hours of delivery to initiate a return, even though you have 30 days to physically return the item.
      </div>

      <h3>Step-by-Step Return Process</h3>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>Step 1: Notify Within 48 Hours</h4>
          <p>Contact us immediately after delivery with your order number and reason for return. This starts the return process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>Step 2: Return Authorization</h4>
          <p>We'll provide a return authorization number and detailed return instructions within 24 hours of your notification.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>Step 3: Package Securely</h4>
          <p>Carefully repackage the item in its original materials. We recommend additional protective wrapping for shipping.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>Step 4: Ship Back</h4>
          <p>Send the item back using the prepaid return label we provide. Must be shipped within 30 days of original delivery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>Step 5: Inspection & Refund</h4>
          <p>Once received, we'll inspect the item and process your refund within 5-7 business days if approved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Return Shipping</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Prepaid Label:</strong> We provide a prepaid return shipping label for standard returns</li>
        <li><strong>Secure Packaging:</strong> Use original packaging plus additional protection we recommend</li>
        <li><strong>Insurance:</strong> All returns are fully insured during transit</li>
        <li><strong>Tracking:</strong> You'll receive tracking information for your return shipment</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Contact for Returns</h3>
      <p>To initiate a return within the 48-hour window:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <strong>info@lunvyr.com</strong> with "RETURN REQUEST" in subject line</li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (929) 728-2394 during business hours</li>
        <li><strong>Include:</strong> Order number, delivery date, reason for return, and photos if applicable</li>
        <li><strong>Response Time:</strong> We'll respond within 4 hours during business days</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>Order Cancellation</h2>
      
      <div class="alert alert-success">
        <strong>Pre-Production Cancellation:</strong> Orders can be cancelled for a full refund before production begins, typically within 48 hours of purchase.
      </div>

      <h3>Cancellation Timeline</h3>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>0-48 Hours After Order</h4>
          <p>Full cancellation and refund available. Order has not yet entered production phase.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>48+ Hours After Order</h4>
          <p>Order enters production. Cancellation may incur restocking fees depending on production progress.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <h4>Production Complete</h4>
          <p>Order ships within 6-8 weeks. Standard return policy applies instead of cancellation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>How to Cancel</h3>
      <p>To cancel your order:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email us at <strong>info@lunvyr.com</strong> with your order number</li>
        <li>Include "CANCELLATION REQUEST" in the subject line</li>
        <li>Provide reason for cancellation (helps us improve our service)</li>
        <li>Refund will be processed within 3-5 business days if approved</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>Damage & Quality Protection</h2>
      
      <div class="alert alert-success">
        <strong>Full Protection:</strong> We stand behind our craftsmanship and ensure your fixture arrives in perfect condition.
      </div>

      <h3>Shipping Damage</h3>
      <p>If your LUNVYR fixture arrives damaged:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Report immediately:</strong> Contact us within 48 hours of delivery</li>
        <li><strong>Document damage:</strong> Take clear photos of packaging and damaged areas</li>
        <li><strong>Keep packaging:</strong> Retain all original packaging materials</li>
        <li><strong>Resolution:</strong> We'll arrange repair, replacement, or full refund</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Manufacturing Defects</h3>
      <p>Rare manufacturing defects are covered under our quality guarantee:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Electrical component failures within 90 days</li>
        <li>Structural integrity issues</li>
        <li>Finish defects not consistent with product description</li>
        <li>Missing components or hardware</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>What's Not Covered</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Normal wear and tear from use</li>
        <li>Damage from improper installation</li>
        <li>Changes in personal preference</li>
        <li>Damage from misuse or accidents</li>
        <li>Electrical issues due to improper wiring</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>Refund Process</h2>
      
      <h3>When Refunds Apply</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Approved returns received within 30 days (with 48-hour notification)</li>
        <li>Order cancelled before production begins</li>
        <li>Item arrives damaged (full replacement or refund)</li>
        <li>Manufacturing defect confirmed by our team</li>
        <li>Our error in order fulfillment</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Refund Amounts</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Full Refund:</strong> Items returned in original condition</li>
        <li><strong>Partial Refund:</strong> Items with minor issues or missing components (case-by-case basis)</li>
        <li><strong>Return Shipping:</strong> Deducted from refund unless item was damaged or defective</li>
        <li><strong>Original Shipping:</strong> Non-refundable unless we made an error</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Refund Timeline</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Processing Time:</strong> 3-5 business days after we receive and inspect the returned item</li>
        <li><strong>Credit Card:</strong> 3-7 business days to appear on your statement</li>
        <li><strong>PayPal:</strong> 1-3 business days</li>
        <li><strong>Bank Transfer:</strong> 5-10 business days</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Restocking Fees</h3>
      <p>Restocking fees may apply in certain situations:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Standard Returns:</strong> No restocking fee for returns notified within 48 hours</li>
        <li><strong>Late Notification:</strong> 15% restocking fee if notification was after 48 hours but item is still returnable</li>
        <li><strong>Custom Elements:</strong> 25% restocking fee for items with any custom modifications</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>Custom Orders</h2>
      
      <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <strong>Limited Returns:</strong> Custom orders have special return conditions due to their bespoke nature.
      </div>

      <h3>Custom Order Return Policy</h3>
      <p>For custom lighting solutions:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>48-Hour Rule Applies:</strong> Must notify within 48 hours of delivery, same as standard orders</li>
        <li><strong>Design Discrepancy:</strong> Returns accepted if final product doesn't match approved specifications</li>
        <li><strong>Quality Issues:</strong> Manufacturing defects or damage covered under standard protection</li>
        <li><strong>Preference Changes:</strong> Not eligible for return once production is approved and completed</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Custom Order Process</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Consultation required:</strong> All specifications confirmed before production</li>
        <li><strong>Design approval:</strong> Technical drawings and material samples provided</li>
        <li><strong>50% deposit:</strong> Required to begin custom work</li>
        <li><strong>Final approval:</strong> You approve final design before production begins</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
      <p>Every custom piece includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Pre-production design approval process</li>
        <li>Regular progress updates with photos</li>
        <li>Final quality inspection before shipping</li>
        <li>Detailed installation instructions and mounting hardware included</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

